  {
    "client_msg_id": "f7c5d46b-d0b8-4f08-9f83-e33b20f58983",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "It would be cute if they found some really robust correlates.\n\nAs for the ego, I read \"A New Kind of Science\" back when it was published.  Found the automata interesting, but the prose intolerable.  A few years later, I met Wolfram.  A little conversation helped me... how to describe it... fashion a pair of neuroatypicality glasses whose filter has helped me enjoy his writing since.",
    "user": "UA14TGLTC",
